Leevi Aaltonen (amụrụ na Jenụwarị 24, 2001) bụ onye Finland na-agba bọọlụ ice hockey nke na-agbara otu KooKoo na Liiga
Ọ gbara bọọlụ asaa maka KalPa n'afọ 2018 na-enweghị ihe mgbaru ọsọ na otu enyemaka.  Ọ bụ New York Rangers dere ya na agba nke ise nke 2019 NHL Entry Draft onye nke otu narị na iri atọ na draft ahụ.
